title: Inaugural Preview, KY Rep. James Comer
itunes:title: Inaugural Preview, KY Rep. James Comer
description:
Guests: Rick Davis, Bloomberg politics contributor, and former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, Drew Littman, Policy Director at Brownstein, Hyatt, Farber, Schreck, and former Chief of Staff for Senator Al Franken, and Rep. James Comer, a Republican representing Kentucky's 1st Congressional District.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
